CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Speaker - The Rev. Horace White of Detroit delivered the principal address at the 23rd anniversary celebration of the Centre Avenue YMCA last Thursday. The Rev. Mr. White is a former member of the Michigan State Legislature. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Reverend Horace White, speaking at banquet table with ten men seated on either side and two tables with men and women in foreground, in Centre Avenue YMCA with flags and curled ribbons hanging from ceiling for twenty-third anniversary celebration
